Name: Cute Blocks
About the game: Cute Blocks.This is a simple arkanoid game. Shoot down blocks with a constantly moving ball and do not let it fly down. All controls with mouse movement. The game uses sophisticated physics, levels of varying complexity and nice drawn girls who will encourage you to win.
